{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for pin code input component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the input text component tokens you want.","","        override var inputTextSizeMaxWidth: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._3000 }","","        override var inputTextSpacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSmall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider: AllIPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(pinCodeInput: CustomPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(pinCodeInput: CustomPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeDimensionSemanticTokensProvider for dimensions","    let pintCodeInputComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own _ and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let pintCodeInputComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.17.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of pin code input"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSPinCodeInput","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllPinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"PinceCodeInputComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"pin code input","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Pin code input","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of dimensions (from "},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/init(spaces:dimensions:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/PinCodeInputComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"